    "detail": "가성비최고입니다 여태까지 묵엇던 호텔중에서 최고. 푸켓에서 두배주고 묵은 다른 호텔보다 나은 깨끗하고 신설건믈. 해먹이랑 수영장 기본시설 다 갖춰져 있고 인테리어도 귀엽고 너무 맘에 들어서 계속 생각나는 호텔. 하루만 있었는데 너무 아쉬웠어요. Great price for value. Definately recommend. Staff was friendly and answered my questions in a very frendly manner. Lots of things to do inside the hotel as well. Well-maintained with quality decorations and facilities. Loved chilling at their hammock with a martini purchased at their mini bar. I would definately revisit if i ever get to go to phucket again. But one thing i found funny was the hotel name, but my thai friend kindly explained the meaning in thai (so confusion was cleared, but it does sound like something else when visitors just read it) Overall, it was best place for value by far among all the places i visited (as an avid travelor). Thanks for making our stay so precious and comfortable :)",
